00:40:08,239 --> 00:40:09,948
<font color="yellow">Baiklah.</font>

548
00:40:10,992 --> 00:40:12,785
<font color="yellow">Kau menang.</font>

549
00:40:20,835 --> 00:40:23,962
<font color="yellow">- Apa yang kau lakukan?
- Kubilang, baiklah.</font>

550
00:40:26,382 --> 00:40:29,218
<font color="yellow">- Jangan lakukan ini, Dale.
- Aku tak melakukan apa pun.</font>

551
00:40:29,385 --> 00:40:31,804
<font color="yellow">Jika kau tinggal,
aku juga tinggal.</font>

552
00:40:31,971 --> 00:40:34,973
<font color="yellow">Dia benar. Kita tahu apa
yang menunggu kita di luar sana.</font>

553
00:40:35,141 --> 00:40:37,101
<font color="yellow">Aku tak ingin menghadapinya
sendiri.</font>

554
00:40:37,268 --> 00:40:40,062
<font color="yellow">Dale, keluarlah.</font>

555
00:40:40,230 --> 00:40:42,481
<font color="yellow">Aku tak ingin kau di sini.</font>

556
00:40:42,649 --> 00:40:45,484
<font color="yellow">Sayang sekali.
Kau tak bisa melakukannya...</font>

557
00:40:45,652 --> 00:40:47,653
<font color="yellow">...memasuki kehidupan seseorang...</font>

558
00:40:47,821 --> 00:40:50,447
<font color="yellow">...membuat mereka menyayangimu
lalu keluar begitu saja.</font>

559
00:40:56,204 --> 00:40:57,996
<font color="yellow">Aku tetap di sini.</font>

560
00:41:00,208 --> 00:41:01,959
<font color="yellow">Masalah telah diselesaikan.</font>

561
00:41:32,740 --> 00:41:34,241
<font color="yellow">Tunggu.</font>

562
00:41:34,409 --> 00:41:35,909
<font color="yellow">Mereka datang.</font>

563
00:41:47,714 --> 00:41:49,506
<font color="yellow">Mereka keluar.</font>

564
00:42:07,066 --> 00:42:09,193
<font color="yellow">Ayolah.</font>

565
00:42:09,360 --> 00:42:12,154
<font color="yellow">Dale, merunduk!</font>

566
00:42:12,322 --> 00:42:16,033
<font color="yellow">Mundur!
Semuanya merunduk!</font>

567
00:42:18,536 --> 00:42:19,828
<font color="yellow">Merunduk!</font>

568
00:43:14,842 --> 00:43:17,803
<font color="yellow">Ayo.</font>

569
00:43:20,932 --> 00:43:22,599
